809
00:40:33.518 --> 00:40:35.171
Katie?

810
00:40:35.215 --> 00:40:37.739
♪ To what I say

811
00:40:37.826 --> 00:40:39.611
You here?

812
00:40:39.741 --> 00:40:43.310
♪ Oh. if you do this.
it'll help you ♪

813
00:40:43.397 --> 00:40:46.705
