there is someone ♪

822
00:41:32.141 --> 00:41:34.970
♪ Up above ♪

823
00:41:43.849 --> 00:41:47.505
♪ Oh. don't you worry

824
00:41:47.592 --> 00:41:51.421
♪ You'll find yourself ♪

825
00:41:51.509 --> 00:41:55.164
